Huawei has announced the local pricing and launch date for its P20 smartphones. The devices – the Huawei P20, P20 Pro, and P20 Lite – will be available at local retailers and mobile operators from 6 April 2018. The official South African pricing for the new lineup is: The Huawei P20 and P20 Pro will be available in Black, Midnight Blue, and Purple Twilight. At its international launch event, Huawei also unveiled its Mate RS Porsche Design – a high-end luxury smartphone. Huawei Product Director Akhram Mohamed told MyBroadband the company is considering bringing the Mate RS to South Africa.